T*
(startYear: release year, from OMDb.) Tj
T*
(genres: list of genres as supplied by OMDb.) Tj
T*
(lead_actors_ids: up to five IMDb actor ids, matched from OMDb actor names with Wikidata.) Tj
T*
(runtimeMinutes: runtime in minutes, from OMDb.) Tj
T*
(averageRating: IMDb average rating, from OMDb.) Tj
T*
(Language: primary language, Wikipedia first, OMDb fallback.) Tj
T*
(Country: production country, Wikipedia first, OMDb fallback.) Tj
T*
(numVotes: number of IMDb votes, from OMDb.) Tj
T*
(budget: production budget in USD millions, from Wikipedia when available.) Tj
T*
(BoxOffice: global box office in USD millions, Wikipedia first, OMDb fallback.) Tj
T*
(plot: short plot summary, from OMDb.) Tj
